  "description": "Mistral Large 3 (675B Instruct 2512 Eagle) is a state-of-the-art general-purpose Multimodal granular Mixture-of-Experts model with 41B active parameters and 675B total parameters trained from scratch with 3000 H200s. This model is the base pre-trained version, not fine-tuned for instruction or reasoning tasks, making it ideal for custom post-training processes. Designed for reliability and long-context comprehension - It is engineered for production-grade assistants, retrieval-augmented systems, scientific workloads, and complex enterprise workflows.\n\nThis model is the Eagle speculator for Mistral Large 3 Instruct. Depending on the task, you can expect noticeable speed-ups on your generations.",
